    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Sociology (Arts)              : Comparative analysis of the process of urbanization in Europe, North America and the Third World; effects of urbanization upon social institutions and individuals; theories of urbanization and urbanism; the Canadian urban system; urban problems in comparative view.          </p>

